Adobe Illustrator x64 -Portable-




1. Double click on "Illustrator_x64_Portable_16.0.2_en_GB.exe" 

2. Browse the directory to extract the files. (Choose a short folder path or you will get errors)

3. Run "StartIllustratorCS6Portable.exe" and Enjoy.

4. IMPORTANT : Don't run at the same time with other Adobe products.
